properties.entry: PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX swivt: <http://semantic-mediawiki.org/swivt/1.0#> PREFIX wiki: <http://smw.coopaxis.fr/id/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> construct { ?x ?r ?y } where { ?x ?r ?y FILTER( ?y != swivt:Subject && ?y != owl:Class && ?y != owl:DatatypeProperty && ?y != owl:ObjectProperty && ?y != owl:Ontology && ?y != rdfs:isDefinedBy && ?r != swivt:wikiNamespace && ?r != swivt:wikiPageModificationDate && ?r != wiki:Attribut-3ADate_de_modification-23aux && ?r != swivt:specialProperty_ASK && ?r != swivt:wikiPageSortKey && !isLiteral(?y) ) } limit 10000
